---
title: St. Jean Baptiste Ultimate Grilled Pork and Poutine with Cheese Curds and Gravy
description: Celebrate St. Jean Baptiste day with a Quebec classic: pork and poutine! Succulent grilled pork gets the perfect side pairing of spring asparagus and hearty roasted potatoes topped with DIY onion gravy and gooey cheese curds!
